      <title><![CDATA[Markdown编辑器Mou中的代码高亮方法]]></title>
      <url>http://yoursite.com/2016/07/04/Markdown%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8Mou%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E9%AB%98%E4%BA%AE%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Mac中Markdown编辑器Mou不支持代码高亮，通过highlight可以将代码高亮显示。</p>
<a id="more"></a>
<p>去<a href="https://highlightjs.org/usage/" target="_blank" rel="external">这里</a>看使用说明，去这里<a href="https://highlightjs.org/download/" target="_blank" rel="external">下载</a>对应的文件。</p>
<p>在使用说明中我们可以看到如下的代码：</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span> <span class="attr">rel</span>=<span class="string">"stylesheet"</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">"/path/to/styles/default.css"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"/path/to/highlight.pack.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="undefined"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="undefined">hljs.initHighlightingOnLoad();</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>第一行href后面引号的内容是你下载文件中存放css文件的路径，第二行src后面的内容是下载的文件中存放hightlight.pack.js的路径。<br>下载下来是一个zip包，解压以后是个文件名为highlight的文件夹，其中css存放在styles文件夹中，在官方有详细说明文档。</p>
<p><strong>示例：</strong><em>把以下代码放入md文件的开头，那么所有的代码在左边显示为高亮的，在styles文件夹中有许许多多的css，即很多显示主题，我这里用的时googlecode，你可以按照自己喜欢的主题更改路径中css的名称。</em></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span> <span class="attr">rel</span>=<span class="string">"stylesheet"</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">"http://yandex.st/highlightjs/8.0/styles/solarized_dark.min.css"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"http://yandex.st/highlightjs/8.0/highlight.min.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="undefined"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="undefined">hljs.initHighlightingOnLoad();</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>效果显示：</strong><em>以下是示例代码</em></p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> re</div><div class="line"> </div><div class="line">p = re.compile(<span class="string">"(\w+)('s|'re|n't)?"</span>)</div><div class="line">wc = &#123;&#125;</div><div class="line">tail_map = &#123; <span class="string">"'s"</span> : <span class="string">'is'</span>, <span class="string">"'re"</span> : <span class="string">'are'</span>, <span class="string">"n't"</span>: <span class="string">'not'</span>&#125;</div><div class="line"> </div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> m <span class="keyword">in</span> re.finditer(p, s):</div><div class="line">    word = m.group(<span class="number">1</span>).lower()                   <span class="comment"># Get the word in lower case</span></div><div class="line">    wc[word] = wc.get(word, <span class="number">0</span>) + <span class="number">1</span>              <span class="comment"># Increase word count</span></div><div class="line">    tail = m.group(<span class="number">2</span>)                           <span class="comment"># Get the word tail</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> tail <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="keyword">None</span>:                        <span class="comment"># If a word tail exists,</span></div><div class="line">        tail = tail_map[tail]                   <span class="comment"># map it to its full form</span></div><div class="line">        wc[tail] = wc.get(tail, <span class="number">0</span>)+<span class="number">1</span>            <span class="comment"># Increase word count</span></div><div class="line"> </div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> (<span class="string">'Total word count: %d'</span>%sum(wc.values())) <span class="comment"># Output the total count</span></div><div class="line">max_len = max(map(len, wc.keys()))              <span class="comment"># Calculate the max length of words for pretty printing</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> w <span class="keyword">in</span> sorted(wc.keys()):                     <span class="comment"># Sort the words</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">print</span> (<span class="string">'%*s =&gt; %d'</span>%(max_len, w, wc[w]))     <span class="comment"># Output</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
