      <title><![CDATA[git命令详解（高级）]]></title>
      <url>http://yoursite.com/2016/07/04/git%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E8%AF%A6%E8%A7%A3%EF%BC%88%E9%AB%98%E7%BA%A7%EF%BC%89/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Git日常应用中的命令，最基本的操作详解。<br><a id="more"></a></p>
<h2 id="Git详解高级"><a href="#Git详解高级" class="headerlink" title="Git详解高级"></a>Git详解高级</h2><h3 id="什么是分支？为何存在？如何创建？如何切换？"><a href="#什么是分支？为何存在？如何创建？如何切换？" class="headerlink" title="什么是分支？为何存在？如何创建？如何切换？"></a>什么是分支？为何存在？如何创建？如何切换？</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">git pull //更新代码</div><div class="line">git branch //查看本地分支，以*开头</div><div class="line">git branch -a //查看所有分支</div><div class="line">git branch new-branch-name //在当前分支的基础上创建新分支</div><div class="line">git checkout new-branch-name //切换到新分支</div><div class="line">git push -u origin new-branch-name //把本地的新分支推送到远程库</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="代码如何合并？遇到冲突怎么解决？"><a href="#代码如何合并？遇到冲突怎么解决？" class="headerlink" title="代码如何合并？遇到冲突怎么解决？"></a>代码如何合并？遇到冲突怎么解决？</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">git checkout new-branch-name</div><div class="line">git pull</div><div class="line">git merge master //把主干的新代码合并到本地，有冲突解决冲突</div><div class="line">git add . //添加新增文件</div><div class="line">git commit -am //添加修改文件，去掉删除文件，提交</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="查看代码提交记录？回溯代码？"><a href="#查看代码提交记录？回溯代码？" class="headerlink" title="查看代码提交记录？回溯代码？"></a>查看代码提交记录？回溯代码？</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">git log -l 5</div><div class="line">git reset HEAD</div><div class="line">git reset -- hard @a232fdfsf334</div><div class="line">git commit -am &quot;message&quot;</div><div class="line">git push -f origin new-branch-name</div><div class="line">git revert @a232fdfsf334</div><div class="line">git push origin new-branch-name</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="gitlab-github-多个git库帐号？推送到多个库"><a href="#gitlab-github-多个git库帐号？推送到多个库" class="headerlink" title="gitlab,github,多个git库帐号？推送到多个库?"></a>gitlab,github,多个git库帐号？推送到多个库?</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">git remote -v</div><div class="line">git remote add gitlab git@gitlab.com/XXX</div><div class="line">git push -u origin gitlab</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    </entry>
    
